name: NYDailyNews
text:
Mysterious China seeds received by dozens of Americans were identified by the USDA as seeds for herbs, vegetables and flowers.

Health departments in all 50 states have warned people not to plant the seeds, no matter how harmless the contents appear to be.

name: NYDailyNews
text:
Bradley McDougald is trying to create his own path with his new team the Jets.

“I can’t be Jamal,” he said. “The only thing I can do is show up every day and be the best Bradley McDougald and hopefully that wins my coaches, my players and the fans over.”

name: NYDailyNews
text:
Sean Penn, 59, reportedly married Vincent D’Onofrio’s 28-year-old daughter, Leila George.

“We are so happy for Leila George and Sean Penn getting married,” wrote philanthropist Irena Medavoy on Instagram. “We love you."

name: NYDailyNews
text:
Mets broadcaster Keith Hernandez asked on air, "What is a PB&J?"

“I know BLT,” Hernandez said to spit-takes from Gary Cohen and Ron Darling. “I’ve never heard a peanut butter and jelly sandwich described like that ... I’m getting out of touch.”
